Description: Python SDK for hardware control on Raspberry Pi CM5 devices
 Provides hardware control and AI capabilities for Distiller devices
 with support for audio, camera, e-ink display, LED control, ASR
 (Parakeet/Whisper), and TTS (Piper). Features Rust-based e-ink
 driver with multi-format image support and intelligent caching. 
